"Work" refers to Gravity Energy, including software, documentation, research materials, and any related assets.

"You" refers to any individual or organization using the Work.

"Non-Commercial Use" means any use that is not for commercial industries, factories, or military applications, and excludes any direct or indirect profit-making activities.

"Improvements" means modifications, enhancements, or derivative works of the Work.



